  "lyrics": {
    "v1": "Savior of the nations, come; Virgin&#39;s Son, here make Thy home! Marvel now, O heav&#39;n and earth, That the Lord chose such a birth.",
    "v2": "Not by human flesh and blood; By the Spirit of our God Was the Word of God made flesh, Woman&#39;s offspring, pure and fresh.",
    "v3": "Wondrous birth! O wondrous Child Of the virgin undefiled! Though by all the world disowned, Still to be in heaven enthroned.",
    "v4": "From the Father forth He came And returneth to the same, Captive leading death and hell High the song of triumph swell!",
    "v5": "Thou, the Father&#39;s only Son, Hast o&#39;er sin the vict&#39;ry won. Boundless shall Thy kingdom be; When shall we its glories see?"
  },
